{"tid":2144650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"陳智思申報持有1個美國物業","createTime":"2020-08-07T16:51:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T03:38:56.000Z","uid":5195,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ea33df58d35f28178e712bad2a39281af20649a4","tid":2144650,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T16:51:30.000Z","msg":"行政會議非官守成員最新嘅利益申報出爐，當中陳智思、史美倫、周松崗同李國章四人都喺外國擁有物業。<br />\n<br />\n根據政府資料，有4名行會非官守成員持有外國物業，其中陳智思持有1個美國物業同1個泰國物業、史美倫持有1個美國物業同1個日本物業、周松崗持有1個英國物業、李國章持有2個英國物業。除此之外，李國章同家人喺香港仲持有32個物業、17個車位同1間酒店。"},{"pid":"a67f3dca610623a800e57b8b8f4de6e0144ed541","tid":2144650,"uid":307619,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-07T16:54:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/72dR15S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F72dR15S.png&h=b2a5a1fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"gold\">無手足 無今日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n手足唔係condom<br />\n開香檳之餘都要記得旁聽</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"a18c9a9c8ddd0326f1dc805a94d1a37626da5083","tid":2144650,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T03:38:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}